PrecisEnactment of a WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL ORDER (NATIONAL PARK - BATHURST ISLAND, N.W.T.) - which provides for (a) the withdrawal from disposal of some 8,700 square kilometres of land located on the northern portion of BATHURST ISLAND, until October 1, 2001, for the establishment of a National Park, and (b) the repeal of a similar but defective Order (P.C. 1996-1562).

precis:
Enactment of a WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL ORDER (NATIONAL PARK - BATHURST
ISLAND, N.W.T.) - which provides for (a) the withdrawal from disposal of
some 8,700 square kilometres of land located on the northern portion of
BATHURST ISLAND, until October 1, 2001, for the establishment of a National
Park, and (b) the repeal of a similar but defective Order (P.C. 1996-1562).
